Swanson Group Aviation, formerly Superior Helicopter,, is a helicopter operating company based in Glendale, Oregon, United States. SGA operates a fleet of Kaman K-MAX helicopters, has an after sales support pilot and engineer services division for aerial firefighting, aerial construction and Unmanned aircraft support. SGA was one of the original launch customers of the Kaman K-MAX, also, supported the USMC in Afghanistan with their partners Kaman and Lockheed Martin with UAS Kmax, and the company is considered one of the most experienced operators of this model having logged over 80,000 flight hours as of 2015.
